der Union,\nleft for Ryder Monday.\nGlasses Relieve\nHEADACHES\nThousands of people drug themselves for\nheadaches, while eye strain is really the cause\nof their headache.\nA scientific eye examination by an Opto\u00ad\nmetrist will disclose the trouble and our head\u00ad\nache glasses will relieve the eye Strain.\nH. L. WINTERS CO.\nf1N 11\nSIMy\nSwukncdBISCUU\nAn, 0tc*S'Os\\\n\u00aba\n1\nI!\n-a*. .JLw\nKUUOURIUIUUUliB\n11\n'P\n.1 \\-j\ni1\nI\nI\n..0- 2 v. \u00bb\u00bb.f v-j i*7\"","height":"24723","width":"17434"}}
